1.0.name: wordpress/gpxplus-widget
1.0.description: This plugin adds a Widget that displays all Pokémons and Eggs in your Global Pokédex Plus(GPXPlus.net) party. This plugin only requires that you know your display name to work, as it will figure out the rest itself.
